{"tid":1550922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公司腦細話同事間唔准講政治！！","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T18:54:47.000Z","uid":189496,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3d30b925e943de8c9bd8905dc82d335cb8684ac6","tid":1550922,"uid":189496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:41:22.000Z","msg":"公司腦細話同事間唔准講政治<br />\n怨上街嘅人搞事搞到佢無生意<br />\n仲對有上街嘅同事態度好差<br />\n仲扣埋同事罷工日人工<br />\n做得好委屈，對住呢啲只顧自己嘅人應該點好？<br />\n<br />\n呢個腦細喺佢個行業有啲名<br />\n不過佢嘅員工就認為佢係出名格衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b91f0ebc15af5688aa8645ea6b78e22c91c6765","tid":1550922,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:41:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d300073f32d7e93a76af7dea913c79756a09139","tid":1550922,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:42:48.000Z","msg":"開名"},{"pid":"cd856f4eb3dc8b0ed9e44d3c11a668942531934c","tid":1550922,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講咁多做